commit.message: dictd: install dictd*.conf files to ${DATADIR}/examples/dictd by default
Fix problems with DICT_CONFIG_PATH and other defined came from Makefile
dict/Makefile: do not copy man page to ${BINDIR} :-)
dict: install samples dict.conf and dict2.conf to ${EGDIR}
index.c: do not use __UNCONST when it is not necessary
dictd: remove option --force|-f as it does nothing (de facto)
dict: fix compilation failure with clang-16.0.6
Disable warningon error SEC_NULL_PTR_DEREF on SunC compiler
Fix linking issue of "dictd" on NetBSD where native estrdup(3) is in -lutil
Fix compilation failure on Darwin-21.6.0 due to deprecated daemon(3)
Fix compilation failure on Darwin-21.6.0 (checks for functions initgroups, getgroups and daemon)
Fix dictfmt compilation failure on Alpine Linux v.3.15.0 with musl libc
